Git config --global user.name  username
Git config --global user.email  email address
Git config --global user.name  show user name 
Git config --global --edit    we can edit user name and email address
Mkdir directory name
git init   initialize the git directory
Git status   yeh status show krta hai what changes happens
Git add file name
Git add. Isse sabhi files add ho jati hai
Git commit -m “initial commit”
Git log show all commit
Git checkout master   bapas se old jagah par aajate hai 
Git checkout hash code   isse us hashcode wale time par ja skte hai 
Git branch    show all branch name
Git branch   branch name    used to add branch name 
Git checkout branch name  isse kisi bhi branch me ja skte hai
Git merge branch name   isse dusri branch ko bhi merge kr skte hai apni branch me
Touch .gitignore   file ke pehle . lagane se file git dwara ignore kar di jati hai





Create repository on github
  Create new repository 
Done







create a new repository on the command line
echo "# git-tricks" >> README.md
git init
git add README.md
git commit -m "first commit"
git branch -M main
git remote add origin https://github.com/swaroopram117/git-tricks.git
git push -u origin main



…or push an existing repository from the command line
git remote add origin https://github.com/swaroopram117/git-tricks.git
git branch -M main
git push -u origin main

